`mongodbatlas..getProjects` describe all Projects. This represents projects that have been created.

> **NOTE:** Groups and projects are synonymous terms. You may find `groupId` in the official documentation.

    orgId: "<ORG_ID>",
    teams: [
        {

            roleNames: [
                "GROUP_READ_ONLY",
